      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained over the years. The engine starts up reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. You may find some minor cosmetic wear, such as small stone chips on the hood and light scuffs on the interior door panels, but the cabin remains clean and smoke-free. It is a dependable driver that performs well in both city and highway conditions, offering a solid balance of reliability and comfort for its next owner.",
