    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking and driving great\u2014honestly, it\u2019s such a smooth experience on the road. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for your next adventure, this is the one! I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how much fun it is to drive. Let's chat!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L straight-six and its signature high-compression ratio and individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a functioning M-Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and a thorough inspection of the rear subframe mounting points. The engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline with no hesitation in the dual-VANOS timing. With a chassis that retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity and a suspension tuned for tactile feedback, this M3 represents a pure, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Reliable daily driver. Clean interior. Engine runs well. Regular service history. Title in hand.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only minor signs of road use such as faint stone chips on the front bumper and a tiny scuff on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple with no tears, and the dashboard remains free of cracks or sun damage. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system and navigation, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The engine idles quietly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes were professionally serviced just last month. It comes with a complete service history, two sets of keys, and high-performance tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a solid, honest vehicle for a buyer who values reliability, comfort, and a clean aesthetic.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
